wb-mqtt-zigbee (1.3.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Rename package from wb-zigbee2mqtt to wb-mqtt-zigbee
  * Add range (slider) controls for writable numerics with min/max

 -- Victor Fedorov <victor.fedorov@wirenboard.com>  Wed, 18 Mar 2026 15:10:00 +0300

wb-zigbee2mqtt (1.2.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add device discovery and real-time state updates from z2m exposes
  * Add expose type mapping: numeric (10 types), binary, enum, text, composite, rgb
  * Add RGB color picker for color lights (HS→RGB via colorsys)
  * Add device removal and rename handling
  * Add MQTT reconnect with full resubscription and device republish
  * Use ieee_address as stable WB device_id

 -- Victor Fedorov <victor.fedorov@wirenboard.com>  Mon, 17 Mar 2026 13:40:00 +0300

wb-zigbee2mqtt (1.1.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add bridge device with 10 controls: state, version, log level, log,
    permit join, device count, last joined, last left, last removed,
    update devices
  * Add en/ru translations for all bridge controls
  * Add bridge log filtering by level (bridge_log_min_level config)
  * Add device event tracking (joined, left, removed)
  * Extract WbZigbee2Mqtt class into app.py

 -- Victor Fedorov <victor.fedorov@wirenboard.com>  Thu, 13 Mar 2026 00:04:00 +0300

